    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/066f8a16571cf8145a54008a727ae273.webp?t=1770919413\" width=600 height=53 /></span><br><br>你——隶属于“Sons of a Gun”组织的孤胆佣兵，每当问题需要靠火力解决时，你就是不二人选。在这片荒芜的星球上，你将面对成群的异形怪物，它们如潮水般涌来，试图吞噬一切。<br><br>但你无所畏惧，手中的枪械是你最忠诚的伙伴。在这片充斥着异形怪物的星球上，你将独自面对无尽的黑暗，用手中的武器，书写属于你的传奇。血与火交织的战场，是你的归宿。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/1481dbb1edc7ef305893e4e6dc7b0acc.poster.avif?t=1770919413\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/1481dbb1edc7ef305893e4e6dc7b0acc.webm?t=1770919413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/1481dbb1edc7ef305893e4e6dc7b0acc.mp4?t=1770919413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/c8d7608350a0d4db41c50c82937662d8.webp?t=1770919413\" width=600 height=53 /></span><br><br>枪林弹雨，火力全开！从咆哮的机枪到精准的狙击步枪，从爆裂的火箭弹到致命的等离子束，数百种武器任你挑选。根据不同的战斗场景，选择最适合的武器。感受等离子枪炙热的能量，将敌人化为灰烬；或者用狙击枪精准地爆头，体验一击必杀的快感。<br><br>时间仿佛在这一刻静止，唯有无尽的杀戮与狂欢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/467bd44525511604ad92eb692031b4a5.poster.avif?t=1770919413\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/467bd44525511604ad92eb692031b4a5.webm?t=1770919413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/467bd44525511604ad92eb692031b4a5.mp4?t=1770919413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/37c2a87f962ee82c4dfbb565c04742ed.webp?t=1770919413\" width=600 height=53 /></span><br><br>从平凡的佣兵，蜕变为传奇英雄。每个角色都拥有独特的成长路径，你可以根据自己的喜好，打造出独一无二的战斗风格。在广袤的宇宙中，隐藏着无数的秘密和宝藏，等待着你去探索。收集强大的装备，提升你的战斗力，让你在战斗中更加所向披靡。 与宇宙中强大的BOSS对决，成就无上荣耀！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/e84c3027aef895612b184243c6ec099a.poster.avif?t=1770919413\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/e84c3027aef895612b184243c6ec099a.webm?t=1770919413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288600/extras/e84c3027aef895612b184243c6ec099a.mp4?t=1770919413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>异星的号角已经吹响，你准备好了吗？孤胆作战，火力全开，在枪林弹雨中书写你的传奇！",
